data.description:
Welcome to this stunning two-story, 4-bedroom residence nestled in the desirable NW neighborhood of Ankeny. The main level boasts
a spacious living room, a modern kitchen with sleek granite countertops and top-tier stainless steel appliances, and an inviting dining
area. Additionally, you'll find a convenient half bath and a well-appointed laundry area on this level.
Upstairs, discover a haven of comfort with four generous bedrooms, including a spacious primary suite complete with a lavish private
bath and abundant storage options. The lower level is thoughtfully finished and presents a fully appointed bar, a fantastic theatre
room, a versatile recreation area/living room, and another convenient half bath.
Step outside to appreciate the delightful pond view from your own backyard, with a rear deck and custom, stamped/stained patio
w/firepit perfect for hosting gatherings and enjoying the outdoors. This home promises an enticing blend of style, comfort, and
entertainment. Don't miss the opportunity to explore this gem—schedule your viewing today and prepare to be captivated.
